    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1Trait" kindref="compound">Trait</ref> is a reference-counted object that can be attached to a <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It shares the lifecycle with the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> it is attached to. When the <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> is destroyed or the attachment is removed, the reference count is decremented. Each <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1Trait" kindref="compound">Trait</ref> type is unique per <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> (one instance per type). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
